    * @Anennya framed the decision as depth-first (fully flesh out CEO/CTO) versus breadth-first (basic elements across all C-suite roles). [33:13]
    * Claude suggested neither approach; instead, build a "spine"—a thin vertical slice tracing consulting or product tracks end-to-end with shared business brief. [1]
